    question: "Is there an AI consultant serving Athens, Alabama?",
    answer: "Yes! Singing River AI provides AI consulting and business automation services throughout Athens, Limestone County, and North Alabama. We're based in the Shoals area and serve the entire I-65 corridor, with Athens being a key service area."
  },
  {
    question: "What types of Athens businesses can benefit from AI?",
    answer: "Virtually any Athens business can benefit from AI automation. We work with manufacturers, healthcare practices, professional services firms, local service businesses, and agricultural operations. The key is identifying where automation saves the most time or captures the most value."
  },
  {
    question: "How much does AI consulting cost for Athens businesses?",
