    question: "Can you help Athens businesses with lead follow-up automation?",
    answer: "Absolutely. Lead follow-up automation is one of our most popular services. We build systems that respond to leads instantly via text and email, qualify prospects automatically, and book appointments—even outside business hours. Most Athens businesses see immediate improvement in lead conversion."
  },
