              <p class="text-stone text-sm">Detailed analysis of your operations with a prioritized plan and realistic ROI projections. Clear expectations before committing.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-display text-2xl mx-auto mb-4">3</div>
