              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-display text-2xl mx-auto mb-4">4</div>
              <h3 class="font-display text-lg mb-2 text-charcoal">Optimization & Growth</h3>
              <p class="text-stone text-sm">Monitor performance, make improvements, and expand capabilities as you see results. Your AI grows with your business.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

